def open_and_analyse(path):
    df = pd.read_csv(path)
    print("-----INFO-----\n")
    display(df.info())
    print("\n----- 3 -----")
    display(df.head(3))
    print("\n----- -----\n")
    display(df.nunique())
    print("\n-----describe-----")
    
    def describe(df):
        #  describe()
        #       
        def na_part(data):
            #     pandas
            part = data.isna().sum() / len(data) * 100
            return part
        return df.describe().append(df.agg([na_part])).transpose()

    display(describe(df))
    print("\n----------")
    display(df.corr())
    return df
